    "synopsis": "A tendril of Hive Fleet Leviathan has reached the Cryptus shieldworlds, the last barrier before Baal itself. On the drowned world of Lysios, where a world-circling tidal wave drags eldritch horrors from the deep, the Adepta Sororitas hold the line against the swarm. Into this nightmare comes a platoon of Tempestus Scions, the Imperium's elite storm troopers, seconded to the enigmatic Inquisitor Ulrich on a mission that may decide far more than one battle: to seize a unique tyranid bioform from the surging tides — a prize Tempestor Chavis and his men may not live to deliver.",
